content: कालक {%<ab>a.</ab>%} Black, dark-blue. --कः {@--1@} A mole, freckle, mark. {@--2@} A water-snake. {@--3@} The black part of the eye. {@--4@} A kind of grain. --का <ab>Ved.</ab> {@--1@} A kind of bird. {@--2@} A daughter of Dakṣa. --कं {@--1@} The liver. {@--2@} An unknown quantity (in <ab>alg.</ab>).
